        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "For even after these many weeks of work there was hardly a single finished article.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56174_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56174/6082_56174_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "\"Ah,\" said Belle, tossing her head, \"you won't find me working myself to death over a Bazaar.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56174_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56174/6082_56174_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "\"Oh, Belle!\" cried Edith, looking shocked.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56174_000015_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56174/6082_56174_000015_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "Why, Edith, as for that you yourself never go down to the North End to see them.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56174_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56174/6082_56174_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "Edith looked so uncomfortable at this suggestion, that Nora, on whom usually fell the duty of taking up the cudgels, exclaimed,",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56174_000020_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56174/6082_56174_000020_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "So trimming her sails she said, \"Why, how silly you are, Nora, you know that I was only in fun.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56174_000021_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56174/6082_56174_000021_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "\"You busy, Belle,\" cried Nora.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56174_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56174/6082_56174_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "\"Indeed I am not,\" was the answer.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56174_000024_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56174/6082_56174_000024_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "For she had twisted the front to the back, had added a deep blue bow to the trimming, and she believed that altogether she had accomplished wonders.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56174_000026_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56174/6082_56174_000026_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "I wish that I could trim hats.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56174_000028_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56174/6082_56174_000028_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "While Nora was talking Belle had been folding up her work, and in a moment more she was putting on her hat and coat.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56174_000029_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56174/6082_56174_000029_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "\"Oh, don't go; you're not mad at Nora, are you?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56174_000030_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56174/6082_56174_000030_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "\"Oh, no, but I think that I ought to be going.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56174_000032_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56174/6082_56174_000032_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "As a matter of fact Belle was deeply offended, and she knew that if she had stayed much longer with her friends she would have been driven to express herself strongly.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56174_000037_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56174/6082_56174_000037_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "\"Better to her face than behind her back.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56174_000039_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56174/6082_56174_000039_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "\"Oh, Edith,\" responded Nora, \"you are altogether too fair.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56174_000041_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56174/6082_56174_000041_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "\"No, it's her grandmother,\" interrupted Edith.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56174_000042_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56174/6082_56174_000042_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "\"No,\" added Brenda, \"it is not.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56174_000043_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56174/6082_56174_000043_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "You make Belle awfully mad sometimes by what you say.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56174_000044_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56174/6082_56174_000044_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "\"Don't let us bicker.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56174_000046_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56174/6082_56174_000046_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "\"Why, Nora, I never heard of such a thing.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56174_000046_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56174/6082_56174_000046_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "Besides I thought that you always wanted to make every one comfortable in her feelings.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56174_000047_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56174/6082_56174_000047_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "But I say that we have had enough of this exchange of compliments for to day.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56175_000000_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56175/6082_56175_000000_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "On the very afternoon when Nora and Belle had their falling out, Julia, after finishing her practising, had gone for a walk.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56175_000000_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56175/6082_56175_000000_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "It was a bright, clear day, and she wished that she had some other girl to walk with her. For when by herself she never ventured beyond the entrance to the park, although if her cousin or one of her school friends could go with her, her aunt had no objection to her walking in the park itself.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56175_000000_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56175/6082_56175_000000_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "One of the disadvantages of her friendship with ruth Roberts lay in the fact that they could seldom be together in the afternoons.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56175_000000_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56175/6082_56175_000000_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "Their homes were too far apart.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56175_000000_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56175/6082_56175_000000_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "It was hard to tell which was the pleasanter thing to do.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56175_000000_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56175/6082_56175_000000_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "At Roxbury, there were Ruth's ponies to drive, and in snowy weather a chance to coast down a quiet side street.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56175_000000_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56175/6082_56175_000000_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "Out of town there are many more chances for fun for girls past sixteen than can possibly be found in town or the city.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56175_000000_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56175/6082_56175_000000_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "She was not fond of music, and she did not pretend to be.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56175_000000_000012",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56175/6082_56175_000000_000012.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "The only matinee that she cared for was the theatre, and as her parent were decidedly opposed to her going often to the play, she could not indulge herself half as much as she wished.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56175_000001_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56175/6082_56175_000001_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "\"To look up and not down, to look out and not in,\" had been one of the lessons which her father had been most careful to teach her.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56175_000001_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56175/6082_56175_000001_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "It was therefore not very often that she let her thoughts dwell too long on her own affairs.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56175_000001_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56175/6082_56175_000001_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "Without realizing it she had walked some distance into the park, and pausing to admire a bit of distant view that she was able to get from a slightly elevated point, she lingered a moment or two longer to decide whether it was an animal or a child that she heard crying behind a small clump of bushes near by.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56175_000001_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56175/6082_56175_000001_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "When she found that there was no other way of satisfying herself, she walked up to the bushes, and there, standing forlornly on three legs, was a tiny Italian greyhound.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56175_000002_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56175/6082_56175_000002_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "\"Why, you poor little thing!\" she cried, \"what is the matter?\" and as she spoke she took the little creature in her arms.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56175_000003_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56175/6082_56175_000003_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "The greyhound showed great joy at the sound of a friendly voice, and looked up in Julia's face with an expression of confidence and gratitude.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56175_000004_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56175/6082_56175_000004_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "\"Come, I am going to put you down on the ground for a minute to see whether you are hurt, or only pretending.\" So, suiting the action to the word, she stood the little dog on its feet.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56175_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56175/6082_56175_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "\"Now let me see if your collar tells who your owner is,\" added Julia, and she bent down towards the dog.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56175_000005_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56175/6082_56175_000005_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "There to her surprise, she read in clear letters, \"Fidessa, Madame du Launy.\" Now immediately Julia decided that the owner of the dog must be the mistress of the large house near the school, about which her friends were so curious.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56175_000005_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56175/6082_56175_000005_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "In an instant, too, she remembered that she had seen this little animal, or one very like it, taking its exercise in front of the great, mysterious house.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56175_000005_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56175/6082_56175_000005_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "\"O, if only it had no owner, what joy!\" she thought, as she gazed into its dark eyes, \"to keep it for myself!\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56175_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56175/6082_56175_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "Nevertheless, she rang the bell bravely, and was welcomed almost with open arms by the serious faced servant who opened the door.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56175_000009_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56175/6082_56175_000009_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "Her figure, though somewhat bent, gave the impression of stateliness.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56175_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56175/6082_56175_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "\"That is an old trick of Fidessa,\" said her mistress smiling, \"when she is at all unhappy she limps about on three legs as if really lame.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56175_000011_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56175/6082_56175_000011_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "She does not know her way about the city, and she is never supposed to go anywhere without her leash.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56175_000011_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56175/6082_56175_000011_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "Fidessa probably jumped out of the carriage to take a walk herself.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56175_000011_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56175/6082_56175_000011_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "For I don't believe that the little thing was actually hiding, and you all three have come back with the report that it was impossible to find her.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6082_56175_000018_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6082/56175/6082_56175_000018_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6082",
        "content": "The footman placed in her hand a little box \"with Madame du Launy's compliments,\" he said.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
